OL,5, Tory peer Michelle Mone is to request a
OL,6, leave of absence from the Lords "to    
OL,7, clear her name", amid allegations she  
OL,8, benefitted from a company she          
OL,9, recommended for a Covid contract.      
OL,11,FIt means she would not attend sittings 
OL,12,Fof the House, vote on any proceedings  
OL,13,For be able to claim any allowance.     
OL,15,FBaroness Mone has been linked to PPE   
OL,16,FMedpro, which won government contracts 
OL,17,Fduring the pandemic.                   
OL,19,FHer spokesman said the allegations had 
OL,20,Fbeen "unjustly levelled against her".  
